Indyrb - Indianapolis Ruby Brigade
Join us to talk about Ruby, work projects, hack on something, or just get a drink or bite & enjoy the company.

Indianapolis, 46250

events.title: January 2026 CINLUG Meeting -- New Generation Of Command-Line Tools
events.description:
CINLUG | Central Indiana Linux Users Group
Are you still using 'grep', 'find', 'less', 'cat', and 'ls'? While these classic Linux core utilities have served us well for decades, the open source world has been busy creating powerful, modern alternatives that offer enhanced features, speed, and user experience.
